EN: That scoundrel dug up the flower bed in my house.

ZH: 这个无赖欺骗了我的信任。
EN: This scoundrel deceived my trust.

ZH: 这种无赖行为不应该被容忍。
EN: Such scoundrel behavior should not be tolerated.

ZH: 那个无赖企图抢劫我。
EN: That scoundrel attempted to rob me.

ZH: 这个无赖大喊大叫，吵得邻居们都无法入眠。
EN: This scoundrel yells and shouts, making the neighbors unable to sleep.

ZH: 这个无赖看起来很凶恶。
EN: This scoundrel looks very ferocious.
